{{Use Australian English|date=August 2018}} {{Use dmy dates|date=August 2018}} {{infobox power station | name = Coonooer Bridge Wind Farm | image = | image_size = | image_caption = | image_alt = | location_map = Australia Victoria | location_map_caption = | location_map_alt = | coordinates ={{coord|-36.4362|143.3616|region:AU-VIC_type:landmark|display=inline,title}} | country = Australia | location = | status = O | construction_began = 2015 | commissioned = 2016 | decommissioned = | cost = | owner = [[Eurus Energy]], [[Windlab]] and the local community | operator = [[Windlab]] | wind_farm_type = Onshore | wind_site_elevation = | wind_site_usage = | wind_site_area = | wind_hub_height = | wind_rotor_diameter = | wind_rated_speed = | ps_units_operational = 6 | ps_units_manu_model = [[Vestas]] V117 | ps_units_uc = | ps_units_planned = | ps_units_cancelled = | ps_units_decommissioned= | ps_electrical_capacity = 20 | ps_electrical_cap_fac = | ps_storage_hours = | ps_annual_generation = | website = https://coonooerbridgewindfarm.com.au/ | extra = }} '''Coonooer Bridge Wind Farm''' is a [[wind farm]] 90km northwest of [[Bendigo, Victoria|Bendigo]] in the Australian state of [[Victoria (Australia)|Victoria]]. Its output is contracted to supply the [[Australian Capital Territory]] via the [[National Electricity Market]] at $81.50 per megawatt hour.<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://www.cmd.act.gov.au/open_government/inform/act_government_media_releases/corbell/2015/wind-auction-result-delivers-renewable-energy-and-economic-benefits-to-the-act |title=Wind auction result delivers renewable energy and economic benefits to the ACT |publisher=[[ACT Government]]|date=6 February 2015|accessdate=2 August 2018}}</ref>
The site is jointly owned by [[Eurus Energy]], [[Windlab]] and the local community. It was the first commercial wind farm in Australia to have the local community included in the ownership in this way.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://coonooerbridgewindfarm.com.au |title=Overview |publisher=Coonooer Bridge Wind Farm Pty Ltd |accessdate=3 August 2018}}</ref>
