The '''Eolica Baia Wind Farm''' is a proposed wind power project in [[Baia, Tulcea|Baia]], [[Tulcea County]], [[Romania]]. The project consists of four individual wind farms connected together. It will have 63 individual [[wind turbine]]s<ref>[http://www.edch.ch/projects/descriptions.shtml Eolica Dobrogea to build wind farms in the Dobrogea region] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090210014204/http://edch.ch/projects/descriptions.shtml |date=2009-02-10 }}</ref> with a nominal output of around 2 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]]. The wind farm will deliver up to 126 MW of power, enough to supply over 75,600 homes with a capital investment required of approximately US$150 million.

