'''Freshwater phytoplankton''' is the [[phytoplankton]] occurring in [[Fresh water|freshwater]] [[ecosystem]]<nowiki/>s.<ref>{{Cite book|title=Ecology of phytoplankton|last=S.|first=Reynolds, Colin|date=2006|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=978-0511191817|location=Cambridge|oclc=76416312}}</ref> It can be distinghuished between limnoplankton ([[lake]] phytoplankton), heleoplankton (phytoplankton in [[pond]]s), and potamoplankton ([[river]] phytoplankton).<ref>{{Cite book|title=The ecology of freshwater phytoplankton|last=S.|first=Reynolds, Colin|date=1984|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=978-0521237826|location=Cambridge|oclc=9442481}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Sandgren|first1=Craig D.|title=Growth and Reproductive Strategies of Freshwater Phytoplankton|date=1988|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=9780521327220|url=https://books.google.com/?id=kVXSSHu1-aoC&printsec=frontcover&dq=freshwater+phytoplankton#v=onepage&q=freshwater%20phytoplankton&f=false|language=en}}</ref>

